  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study is conducted in Europe. The study aims to observe the incidence of
      serious adverse drug reactions in subjects with type 2 diabetes during Levemir® treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
